      <title>阿达尼·格林制定了偿还 7.5 亿美元债券的计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-08/adani-green-lays-out-initial-plan-for-repaying-750-million-bond</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿达尼集团旗下太阳能部门公布了偿还明年到期的 7.5 亿美元债券的初步蓝图，随着这家印度企业集团在今年早些时候市场暴跌后重建信心，债务上涨势头得以延续。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-08/adani-green-lays-out-initial-plan-for-repaying-750-million-bond</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Dec 2023 02:23:09 GMT</pubDate>
