    <item>
      <title>由于 OPEC+ 未能阻止油价暴跌，油价陷入 2018 年以来最严重的跌势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-8</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五油价上涨，但由于对全球供应过剩的担忧，油价仍将录得自 2018 年以来最长的单周下跌，交易员怀疑 OPEC+ 进一步减产能否成为有效的解决方案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-8</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 23:49:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着复苏的消退，2024年中国石油需求增长将放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/china-s-oil-demand-growth-is-seen-cooling-in-2024-as-pandemic-recovery-fades</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着三年大流行后被压抑的旅行和消费需求的影响开始消退，中国明年的石油需求增长将放缓，这给本已令人失望的 2024 年全球前景蒙上阴影。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/china-s-oil-demand-growth-is-seen-cooling-in-2024-as-pandemic-recovery-fades</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 23:36:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
